Dummy backend, for testing purposes.

Dummy backend, for testing purposes. As the Fft_backend base class throws "unimplemented" in all its out_of_place and in_place functions, we merely override those here as no-ops, since this makes testing easier.

These numbers are 'number-of-times' constants as they map to FFTW planning strategies. We list them here since they are used outside the FFTW backend, too (CVSIP).

number-of-times >= 32 or 0 (infinity)... patient number-of-times >= 12 .................. measure else ................................... estimate
